Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.97,0:00:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
