Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.70,0:01:04.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.11,0:01:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好去捉水母了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go jelly fishing?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  那还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, am I
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.15,0:01:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,网给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your net
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母可不会自己捉自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The jellyfish don't catch themselves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得先收好我的秘密盒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I have to put away my secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密盒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret box?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.07,0:01:23.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没跟我说过你有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:23.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never told me about your
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.74,0:01:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密盒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  偷窥狂宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hands off, Peeping Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.87,0:01:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这秘密盒可是我专属的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's my secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且要是我给你看了里面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, if I showed you what was inside
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能算秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be a secret anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.83,0:01:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你能看到我秘密盒里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only you could see inside my secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的一生都将会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it would change your life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对秘密了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know all about secrets
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.31,0:01:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有超多的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a gazillion secrets
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知秘密最好的一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's no secret that the best thing about a secret
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是秘密地把自己的秘密告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is secretly telling someone your secret
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从而秘密地再把一个秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thereby secretly adding another secret
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收藏到秘密的秘密收藏里去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to their secret collection of secrets
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,secretly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要听我一个秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to hear one of my secrets?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.63,0:02:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道你是我最好的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you know you're my best friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来听一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hear another one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.90,0:02:22.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:22.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,悄悄讲  我有点幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secretly, I'm a little bit naive
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对你大为改观了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'll never look at you the same way again, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再跟我讲点秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me some more secrets
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱我在蟹堡王的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l love my job at The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我睡觉都穿鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sleep with my shoes on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢面包两面都涂果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l like jelly on both sides of my toast
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有本借书逾期了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've got an overdue library book
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得捉水母跟吹泡泡就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l think jelly fishing and bubble blowing are the
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班从没迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never been late for work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟人讲话说过花哨两字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've said the word "fancy" in conversation
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢听装卸区公告跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l like to dance to loading zone announcements
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没有拿到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l still don't have my driver's license
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点太矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm a little on the short side
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就穿着三条内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm wearing three pairs of underwear right now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gasp
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜都猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never would have guessed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我看你秘密盒里的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, will you show me what's inside your secret box?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我才能知道  不能让你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt's for me to know, and for you to never find out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你是能一眼被看穿  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may be an open book, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我可比你那情况更复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm a bit more complicated than that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我内心深不可测的城府可神秘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The inner machinations of my mind are an enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:22.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,574)}牛奶
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.85,0:03:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒也有不少秘密玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I got plenty of secret stuff, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我穿了秘密袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got my secret socks on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,890)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有秘密小蜗食盆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my secret Gary's bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My secret TV
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有秘密电视频道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my secret TV channel
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think of that, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是里面的东西让你给看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you saw what was inside
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会知道它为什么就得是秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd know why it has to be secret
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这特别的盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Inside this very box
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是整个秘密国度中最秘密的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the most secrety secret in all of Secretdom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我正是它唯一的见证者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I am its sole witness
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是个重担  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a heavy burden, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是谁都不能知道这盒子的神秘之处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but nobody must know the mystery of the box
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥家都不能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's house
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一刻都不能停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a full-time job
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要时刻保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm constantly on the alert
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道会有谁会突然要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never know when someone's gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这是想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的秘密盒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now hand it over
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是派大星  我必须得知道秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Patrick, I must know the secret
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你讲最后一遍  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the last time, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  就一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, just a peek
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然到这种地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, it's come to this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亏我们还加了永远好朋友俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to think we joined the Best Friends Forever Club
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着  偷秘密宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, SpongeBob "Secret Stealer" Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你再来靠近我的秘密盒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you ever come near my secret box again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we won't be friends anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're supposed to be
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,friends forever
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768,568)}海绵宝宝                    派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我内心好龌龊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel so filthy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我玷污了我们的友谊园林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have soiled our friendship garden
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只是忍不住而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't help myself
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道那是你的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know it's your secret
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证会尊重的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise to respect that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你原谅我吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能全怪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not all your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟这可是个特别棒的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, this is a pretty great secret
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.30,0:06:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一般人完全抗拒不了最棒的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, how could you resist the greatest secret ever?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mysterious
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.44,0:06:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最强大的秘密  裤头村独有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,powerful secret in all of Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么说  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个盒子里有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could be in that box
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星居然还不让我开盒看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Patrick doesn't want me to see?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是全世界唯一一只白化水母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the world's only albino jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可能派大星是个珠宝大盗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or maybe Patrick's a master jewel thief
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盒里满是钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's full of diamonds
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可能派大星是个发神经的疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Patrick's a deranged maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会把受害人的断头装进盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who keeps his victims' severed heads in a box
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or even worse
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.38,0:06:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是我圣诞节派对时的丑照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe it's an embarrassing snapshot of me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from a Christmas party
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要知道秘密盒里有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l got to find out what's in that secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道就不睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to rest till I do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么看秘密盒里的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you look into a secret box?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然是要秘密地看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secretly, of course
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要在派大星睡着的时候拿走盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just take the box while Patrick's sleeping
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往盒子里面看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look inside
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁派大星没来得及注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and before Patrick even has time to notice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷偷溜回去还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll slide it back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星就发现不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick won't know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我自己又多了一份秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll have my own little secret
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是好办法啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, eh, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你懂个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就一蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a snail
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,磨来磨去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snizzlefrazzy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.07,0:07:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Se-e-ecret
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得再安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to be more quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能让派大星醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to wake Patrick up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1072,452)}薯片
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密盒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good old secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看里面有什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what's inside
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了  小盒盒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nighty-night, boxie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星还真睡得挺沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Patrick sure is a heavy sleeper
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.16,0:10:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蛤蜊神偷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the clam burglar
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在偷我的秘密盒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he's stealing my secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我交出来  秘密盒抢匪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand over the goods, secret-box bandit
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.47,0:10:29.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备迎接你一生中最难受的枕头大战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and prepare for the most unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pillow fight of your life
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.56,0:10:31.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:31.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少来了  大盗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, burglar
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But SpongeBob's my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他从来就不会偷我东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he'd never steal from me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是我  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.17,0:10:42.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:42.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是永远好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the Best Friends Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远好朋友戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best Friends Forever Ring
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,友情戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our friendship ring
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我这么说能让你好受些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If it makes you feel any better
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没看里面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't looked inside
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经越过底线了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have crossed the line
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.99,0:11:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  这份友情结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As of right now, this friendship is over
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假的  真的想看你就看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, you can look inside if you really want to
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我一生中最激动的时刻之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is one of the most exciting moments of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要开盒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一根线头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a string
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密线头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A secret string
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那没事了  你说是就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, when you're right, you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你秘密盒里就那玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's some secret box you got there
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for showing me that
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, good night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have known
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直都只是根线头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it was just a piece of string all along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要跟小蜗讲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait till I tell Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好他没有把秘密线头拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing he didn't pull the secret string
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.20,0:12:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开我秘密盒里的秘密夹层
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,opening the secret compartment of my secret box
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.52,0:12:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让海绵宝宝圣诞派对的丑照给露出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,revealing one embarrassing snapshot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of SpongeBob at that Christmas party
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.31,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(272,435)}怪才乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,296)\frz20.27}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.27\pos(414,660)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:36.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.27\pos(412,280)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.27\pos(322,334)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.27\pos(486,664)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是街边那家宠物医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're with the pet hospital down the street
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说你家里有只动物快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have a dying animal on the premises
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.13,0:12:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你正在向被忽略的天才家里通话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've reached The House of Unrecognized Talent
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请听到声音后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please start after the
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着好像你得处理一只快死了的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds as though you've got a dying animal to attend to
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eh, old chum?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.64,0:13:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐班的章鱼威廉花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squilliam Fancyson from band class?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说你现在在耍收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear you're playing the cash register now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一字眉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's the unibrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可大可值钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's big and valuable
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.02,0:13:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是个豪华大乐队的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm the leader of a big fancy band now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周就要到泡泡碗去演出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're supposed to play the Bubble Bowl next week
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Bu-Bu-Bu
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的梦想生活被我抢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm living your dreams, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题就在于我下周没空  来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The problem is, I'm busy next week and can't make it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你跟你乐队能帮忙替一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, I was hoping you and your band could cover for us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-I'd, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你连个乐队都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't even have a band
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.69,0:13:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  不打扰你继续当服务生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just let you get back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the service industry now
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.84,0:13:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我碰巧已经不卖快餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It just so happens that I don't sell fast food
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实有个乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do have a band
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡碗的演出我们可是去定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're gonna play that Bubble Bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊  花花小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you like that, Fancyboy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周二祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck next Tuesday
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望观众都带足了布洛芬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope the audience brings lots of ibuprofen
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得赶紧招个游行乐队来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've got to drum up a marching band fast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:18.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(710,918)}鼓
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.21,0:14:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drum
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐队笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Band humor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:27.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,174)}快看这个
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要充实你的枯燥生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Looking to add fulfillment to your dull, dull life?"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就加入最棒的音乐明星团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Then become part of the greatest musical sensation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轰动裤头村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever to hit Bikini Bottom"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:38.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(860,304)}烘培坊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.09,0:14:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被成千上万的陌生人永远崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"And be forever adored
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by thousands of people you don't know"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.43,0:14:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更不必说免费小点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Not to mention free refreshments"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚开始练习  八点半准时到达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Practice begins tonight, 8:30 sharp"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋乐器出租员害我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid music rental clerk made me late
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那古板三叶虫连双簧管跟手肘都不分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That trilobite didn't know an oboe from an elbow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.95,注释,,0,0,0,,[ oboe（双簧管）与 elbow（手肘）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.41,0:14:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手肘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elbow
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是乐队笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More band humor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People, people
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Settle down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有多少先前耍过乐器的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many of you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have played musical instruments before?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刑具算不算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do instruments of torture count?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋黄酱算乐器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is mayonnaise an instrument?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不算  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋黄酱不算乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mayonnaise is not an instrument
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣根酱也不算乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horseradish is not an instrument either
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  没人有经验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's fine, no one has any experience
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.72,0:15:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我天赋异禀  足够教你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I have enough talent for all of you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.56,0:15:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么时候领免费小点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When do we get the free food?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  跟着我吹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, try to repeat after me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铜管乐器组  起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brass section, go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,木管乐器组
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now the wind
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the drums
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜没杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad that didn't kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来试试跟上节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just try stepping in rhythm
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要大家站成五人一排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I want everyone to stand in straight rows of five
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是不是要开始踢腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ls this the part where we start kicking?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,歌舞队才那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a chorus line
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kicking?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要踢腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to do some kicking
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I ought to
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开白色轿车的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever's the owner of the white sedan
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘记关车灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you left your lights on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的各位  非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's perfect, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡碗  我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bowl, here we come
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旗手  把旗子舞好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flag twirlers, really spin those things
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, turn
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旗手  快上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flag twirlers, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要看你们舞好旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to see some spinning
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旗手  舞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flag twirlers, let's move
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.20,0:16:59.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:16:59.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.83,0:17:00.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:00.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第三天
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口琴独奏怎么样了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that harmonica solo coming, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大有可为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's tremendous
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to see?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第四天
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我们演出前集合的最后一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is our last night together before the show
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你们打一开始就毫无长进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I know that you haven't improved since we began
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我有个理论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I have a theory
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人们想表现聪明就会大声说话  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People talk loud when they want to act smart, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Correct
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以要是我们演奏声音大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if we play loud
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人就可能会觉得我们水平高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,people might think we're good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a-one and a-two
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a-one, two, three, four
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  新理论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, new theory
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可能该演奏得非常小声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should play so quietly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小到听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no one can hear us
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许要想演奏得不那么难听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe we wouldn't sound so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些人就不应该瞎耍大肉钳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if some people didn't try to play with big, meaty claws
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚在说什么  混账
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say, punk?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.19,0:18:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,meaty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,claws
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这大肉钳可不单单是用来求偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, these claws ain't for just attracting mates
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来  老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这样  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, people
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.62,0:18:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都明智点  别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's be smart and bring it off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在连会说话的奶酪都要来训我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So now the talking cheese is going to preach to us
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道局势很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know tensions are high
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.96,0:19:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐器交了押金的  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a deposit on that equipment, people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你们静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Settle down, please
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Class is over
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah, see ya tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.22,0:19:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下课后你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, what are you doing after
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you did it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们夺走了我奔向快乐的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You took my one chance at happiness
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也粉碎了这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and crushed it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉碎成一片片细小微小极小的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crushed it into little, tiny, bite-size pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的对你们寄予了更高的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really had expected better of you people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我连期望都失败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm a loser for that, too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天不用麻烦你们过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't bother showing up tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.84,0:20:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟主办方说你们排练出事故死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just tell them you all died in a marching accident
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到底是什么样的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of monsters are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个可怜人在有需要时向我们求助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That poor creature came to us in his hour of need
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们却让他失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we failed him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.37,0:20:19.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥方便时总会出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's always been there for us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when it was convenient for him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃芙琳  你家小吉米困在火场的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evelyn, when your little Jimmy was trapped in a fire
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who rescued him?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fireman
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.40,0:20:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你因为美黑药而心脏骤停的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when your heart gave out from all those tanning pills
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁救活了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who revived you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救护车上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some guy in an ambulance
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.82,0:20:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那如果我们都假装章鱼哥是消防员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, if we all could just pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Squidward was a fireman
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者救护车上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or some guy in an ambulance
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么大家一定就能够团结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then I'm sure we could all pull together
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.49,0:20:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找出加入乐队的真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and discover what it truly means
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be in a marching band
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  为了消防员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for the fireman
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让章鱼哥抬起头来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's make Squidward proud
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-one, a-two
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a squiddly-diddly do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,766)}泡泡碗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道会这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew this was going to happen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主办方非得另外再找个乐队不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're just going to have to find another band to play
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(870,588)}乐队入口
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just hope that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼威廉没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squilliam doesn't find out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squilliam
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只是要看你出丑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to watch you blow it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  你乐队在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, where's your band?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They couldn't come
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,died
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be my band
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们准备好表演了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready to perform, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.72,0:21:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.74,0:21:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你乐队在我心目中刚好就这模样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is exactly how I pictured your band would look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是人家的热切表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's his eager face
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.27,0:21:39.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这应该是我最后一次在这镇上露面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this will be the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can show my face in this town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  球迷们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, football fans
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.39,0:21:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掌声有请裤头村超级乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,put your hands together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the Bikini Bottom Super Band
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些鱼长得可真是丑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are some ugly-looking fish
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能我们在一家有毒的垃圾场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're near one of those toxic-waste dumps
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to be sick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.15,0:22:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.18,0:22:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.72,0:22:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,four
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜者获一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The winner takes all
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正是追击的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the thrill of one more kill
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.11,0:22:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屹立到最后的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The last one to fall
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,决不会灰心丧志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will never sacrifice their will
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.93,0:22:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要回头看  那逼近的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't ever look back on the world closing in
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.77,0:23:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不懈地战斗  在风中展翅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be on the attack with your wings on the wind
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.98,0:23:05.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:05.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, the games will begin
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.44,0:23:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是甜蜜  甜蜜的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's sweet, sweet, sweet victory, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.54,0:23:19.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任由我们去争取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:19.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's ours for the taking
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我们奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's ours for the fight
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.08,0:23:29.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这甜蜜  甜蜜的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:29.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the sweet, sweet, sweet victory, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.05,0:23:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终有人屹立到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the one who's last to fall
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.52,0:23:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甜蜜的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet, sweet, sweet victory
